OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FBy Westminster Producer Elisa Menendez
OL,9,FThe issue of maternity pay in the UK
OL,10,Fhas been thrown into the spotlight
OL,11,Fafter Conservative leadership hopeful
OL,12,FKemi Badenoch appeared to suggest it
OL,13,Fwas currently "excessive".
OL,15,FDespite later insisting she does
OL,16,Fbelieve in maternity pay, her comments
OL,17,Fhave sparked backlash from opponents
OL,18,Fand campaigners, with the latter
OL,19,Fsaying many mothers are forced to cut
OL,20,Ftheir leave early because statutory
OL,21,Fpay isn't enough anymore.
