OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FWhat is the controversy surrounding
OL,8,Fmaternity pay?
OL,10,FDuring an interview with Times Radio
OL,11,Fon Sunday, Shadow Communities
OL,12,FSecretary Ms Badenoch described
OL,13,Fstatutory maternity pay as "a function
OL,14,Fof tax", adding: "Tax comes from
OL,15,Fpeople who are working ` we're taking
OL,16,Ffrom one group of people and giving to
OL,17,Fanother. This, in my view, is
OL,18,Fexcessive."
