OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,F"The exact amount of maternity pay, in
OL,8,Fmy view, is neither here nor there. We
OL,9,Fneed to make sure that we are creating
OL,10,Fan environment where people can work
OL,11,Fand people can have more freedom to
OL,12,Fmake their individual decisions."
OL,14,FFollowing fierce backlash, she later
OL,15,Fclaimed she was misinterpreted and she
OL,16,Fdoes support maternity pay.
