OL,7,FWhen asked what she would do to boost
OL,8,Ffalling birth rates, she told an event
OL,9,Fat the Conservative Party Conference
OL,10,Fon Monday that people are "scared to
OL,11,Fhave families" and "we should find a
OL,12,Fway to make life easier for those who
OL,13,Fare starting families".
OL,15,F"Some people feel that they can't
OL,16,Fafford children, I often think that
OL,17,Ftoo many people are worried about the
OL,18,Fmoney more than they need to be," she
OL,19,Fadded, as she listed concerns around
OL,20,Fbirth trauma, childcare and housing as
OL,21,Fcompounding factors.
