OL,7,F'Too many people are worried about the
OL,8,Fmoney more than they need to be'
OL,10,FWhat is statutory maternity pay and
OL,11,Fhow long do you need to be at a
OL,12,Fcompany to qualify?
OL,14,FStatutory maternity pay is paid for up
OL,15,Fto 39 weeks (approximately nine
OL,16,Fmonths) and usually starts at the
OL,17,Fbeginning of the agreed maternity
OL,18,Fleave period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
