OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FFor the first six weeks, new mums
OL,8,Freceive 90% of their average weekly
OL,9,Fearnings before tax. After that, they
OL,10,Freceive #184.03 or 90% of average
OL,11,Fweekly earnings - whichever is lower -
OL,12,Ffor the next 33 weeks.
OL,14,FThe employee must also earn on average
OL,15,Fat least #123 per week to qualify. Tax
OL,16,Fand National Insurance are deducted
OL,17,Ffrom the payments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
