OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FMaternity Action said "woefully
OL,8,Finadequate levels" of statutory
OL,9,Fmaternity pay are even driving women
OL,10,Fto use food banks for the first time
OL,11,Fduring their pregnancy and maternity
OL,12,Fleave.
OL,14,F"The #184.03 weekly statutory
OL,15,Fmaternity pay and maternity allowance
OL,16,Fare currently worth less than half
OL,17,F(46%) the #400.40 that someone on the
OL,18,Fhigher rate national minimum wage
OL,19,Fwould be paid for working a 35-hour
OL,20,Fweek, and less than a third of women's
OL,21,Faverage full-time earnings," it added.
