OL,7,FCampaigners and critics - including
OL,8,FBadenoch's Tory leadership rival
OL,9,FRobert Jenrick - point out that
OL,10,Falthough the UK's length of paid leave
OL,11,Fis longer than many of its
OL,12,Finternational counterparts, the pay is
OL,13,Fmuch lower.
