OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FYes. It is at the discretion of an
OL,8,Findividual employer if they offer
OL,9,Femployees a greater maternity or
OL,10,Fpaternity package and many do.
OL,12,FThe Chartered Institute of Personnel
OL,13,Fand Development (CIPD) found that 18%
OL,14,Fof the 2,000 surveyed between June and
OL,15,FJuly 2022 offer between four and 13
OL,16,Fweeks of enhanced maternity pay at or
OL,17,Fnear the full rate of pay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
