OL,3,CThe facts around UK maternity pay
OL,4,Cafter Badenoch suggests it's
OL,5,C'excessive'
OL,7,FHowever, according to Maternity Action
OL,8,Fthe number of employers offering
OL,9,Fbetter terms has been falling in
OL,10,Frecent years. It says just over 10% of
OL,11,Fwomen benefit from additional
OL,12,Fmaternity pay from their employers.
OL,14,FHow much does it cost businesses?
OL,16,FEmployers can reclaim 92% of
OL,17,Femployees' statutory maternity and
OL,18,Fpaternity pay. Small businesses that
OL,19,Fqualify for small employers' relief
OL,20,Fcan reclaim 103%.
